message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $13,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your valuation of the product. I am willing to pay $12,000 for the product.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $12,750?
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. Considering the value of the product, I would like to propose a price of $12,500.
